test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 779 == -779
 +  where 779 = <built-in function prod>([-779, -1])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7123641de300>([-779])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7123641de300> = [[-779, 1, -779], [-779, 1, -779], [-779, 1, -779], [-779, 1, -779], [-779, 1, -779], [-779, 1, -779]].count
